OL,3,CSixth man charged with murder after
OL,4,Cstreet attack
OL,6,FA sixth person has been charged with
OL,7,Fmurder following the death of a man
OL,8,Fwho was attacked in the street.
OL,10,FSuhail Choudry, 35, died three days
OL,11,Fafter he was allegedly chased and
OL,12,Fassaulted by a group of men armed with
OL,13,Fweapons including sticks and bats in
OL,14,FFlasby Street, Keighley, on 8 February.
OL,16,FWaseem Islam, 39, of East Avenue,
OL,17,FKeighley, was arrested on Wednesday, 6
OL,18,FMay, and has now been charged with
OL,19,Fmurder. He was due to appear at
OL,20,FBradford Magistrates' Court on
OL,21,FThursday.
